---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy — Viktor Holovin">
  <section class="prose prose-invert max-w-3xl mx-auto py-14">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>
      This website is a personal portfolio for Viktor Holovin, Static Site Developer.  
      I respect your privacy and keep this policy simple:
    </p>

    <h2>Information I Collect</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>I do not collect personal data directly through this website.</li>
      <li>Basic, anonymous analytics may be used to understand site traffic (e.g., page visits).</li>
      <li>If you contact me by email or Upwork, I will receive the information you share (such as your name, email, and project details).</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How Your Information Is Used</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>I use the information you provide only to respond to your inquiries and potential project discussions.</li>
      <li>I do not sell or share your personal information with third parties.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>
      If you hire me through Upwork, your data is handled under Upwork’s policies.  
      If you email me directly, standard email providers may process that information.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      For any privacy-related questions, you can contact me at:  
      <a href="mailto:viktor@holovin.com">viktor@holovin.com</a>
    </p>

    <p class="mt-10 text-sm opacity-70">
      Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString()}
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
